				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-l%C3%A2n/poem-fyO4kwrEP368Ie-OOZ_eAg">Bắc lân - 北鄰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/B%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-c%C3%A1o/poem-mLEGY5d9nFI0RH280X-vIQ">Bình Ngô đại cáo - 平吳大告</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-%C3%A1i-ch%C3%BAng/poem-vRbxRLFOPBjm83wKLfI8Qw">Phiếm ái chúng - 泛愛眾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A1i-L%C3%B4-T%E1%BB%AD/poem-dndCdLNBu6u8MqFo2vsRmQ">Tái Lô Tử - 塞蘆子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thu-ph%E1%BB%91-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-11/poem-fHsP1LhDwRSlxmuRKWOyEQ">Thu phố ca kỳ 11 - 秋浦歌其十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BB%B7-H%E1%BB%99i-%C4%91%E1%BB%99/poem-jqVx_0LhhyA9FFdO-I_N0w">Thuỷ Hội độ - 水會渡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/T%E1%BB%A9-Ti%C3%AAu-V%C5%A9/poem-bAUZty7kpHYXKfs8k-ISCg">Tứ Tiêu Vũ - 賜蕭瑀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/author-19Y6ZR7qO5ib1Hce98JOUQ">Lý Thế Dân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
